OL,3,CMarginal improvement in consumer
OL,4,Cconfidence in March
OL,6,FThere was a marginal improvement in
OL,7,Fconsumer confidence in March, amid a
OL,8,F"fragile" outlook for the year ahead,
OL,9,Ffigures show.
OL,11,FGfK's long-running Consumer Confidence
OL,12,FIndex increased by one point to minus
OL,13,F19, with expectations for the general
OL,14,Feconomic situation over the next 12
OL,15,Fmonths improving by two points to
OL,16,Fminus 29 ` six points lower than a
OL,17,Fyear ago.
