OL,4,Cconfidence in March
OL,6,FExpectations for personal finances
OL,7,Fover the next 12 months fell by one
OL,8,Fpoint to positive one, while the major
OL,9,Fpurchase index, a measure of
OL,10,Fconfidence in buying big ticket items,
OL,11,Fremained unchanged at minus 17, 10
OL,12,Fpoints better than last March.
OL,14,FNeil Bellamy, consumer insights
OL,15,Fdirector at NIQ GfK, said: "Consumer
OL,16,Fconfidence remains subdued with a
OL,17,Fheadline score of minus 19 for March.
